# 🧠 AI Note Taking App — Complete Production Development Plan

> **Stack Confirmed from Codebase**: Express 5, TypeScript (ESM), Prisma ORM, PostgreSQL, Zod, JWT via `jsonwebtoken`, bcrypt, cookie-parser. The `aiAgent/` directory exists but is empty — this plan fills it in.

