## 13. Resume Description

**AI-Powered Note Taking Assistant** | Node.js · TypeScript · PostgreSQL · Google Gemini API

- Architected a full-stack AI note-taking application featuring an **agentic workflow** powered by Google Gemini's function-calling API, enabling users to manage notes entirely via natural language.
- Engineered a **multi-tool AI agent** capable of creating, searching, updating, and completing notes from conversational prompts, reducing friction by eliminating manual UI interactions.
- Designed a **secure, scalable REST API** with JWT authentication (HTTP-only cookies), Zod schema validation, and per-user rate limiting to protect AI endpoints.
- Built a **PostgreSQL relational schema** via Prisma ORM with optimized indexing, supporting full-text search and structured user-note relationships.
- Implemented **prompt injection defense** through system prompt hardening, input sanitization, and a tool-calling architecture that constrains AI output to predefined schemas.

